  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the steamer to 200 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Season the tilapia fillets with salt and pepper.",
    "Wrap each tilapia fillet in a banana leaf.",
    "Steam the wrapped fish for 8 minutes.",
    "Prepare the caramel sauce by heating it in a saucepan over low heat.",
    " Warm the bamboo trays by wrapping them in a damp cloth and microwaving for 20 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by placing a steamed fish fillet on each bamboo tray.",
    "Drizzle the caramel sauce over the fish and top with mixed greens and chopped cilantro.",
    "Serve the tacos immediately, garnished with a squeeze of lime juice."
